from pyspark.sql.functions import avg

# Perform the aggregation after renaming columns

    avg("`Fat (g)`").alias("avg_fat"),
    avg("`Protein`").alias("avg_protein"),
    avg("`Carb. (g)`").alias("avg_carb"),

).show()
